I"Ï	<p>Welcome to Classical Mechanics II. This course will expand on the ideas of Classical Mechanics I by talking about mechanics of many particle systems.</p>

<p>The prerequisites are as follows:</p>
<ol>
  <li>A working knowledge of classical mechanics I</li>
  <li>A working knowledge of ordinary differential equations</li>
</ol>

